{"tid":2491703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有有口臭或者身邊朋友有口臭既人","createTime":"2021-04-16T13:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T14:47:54.000Z","uid":286199,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f26b48e690fbb2a609ab87adb0ec741c6dfd4b3e","tid":2491703,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都有口鼻問題，係臭撚到自己都聞到嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想知自己有冇口臭好簡單，嘟個上唇埋個鼻度聞，臭既話即係有口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 身邊有朋友口臭既ching，辛苦你了，不論係男係女都好，我可以代替你朋友比你屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為有口臭真係好撚抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n 我試過唔同辦法處理口臭，試過刮條臭閪脷，大力少少就損撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又試過臭口水，不過呢兩種方法都係治標唔撚治本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 到呢度，呢個po既重點來了，就係教大家點撚樣醫口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係用       <span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">梳打粉</span></strong></span>𠺘口&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用既份量其實係用少少就得，大概一粒仔左右，同埋刷牙既時候用牙刷既後面既凹凸位刮埋條臭閪脷，如果你支牙刷冇凹凸位既，通常d毛都係好撚硬，建議買過第2隻牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 最後，如果你地care有口臭既朋友既話，麻煩你send埋呢個po比佢地。<br />\n  <br />\n  其實用梳打𠺘口個感覺同用鹽𠺘口既感覺好似，我覺得d廢佬話用鹽𠺘口有用，其實可能只係傳傳下傳撚錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 以下留言歡迎屌我口臭<br />\n 利申：已經唔臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268524c3dcb14e96d2aea6b9e8e9552d9026234b","tid":2491703,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"你地頂得順口臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3b120d6c10cd0bff2753fcf3787fc4af2e042a","tid":2491703,"uid":286199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:29:32.000Z","msg":"個口咁撚臭，含到碌尻都臭埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eab14012f7f5bd6043957d0e8d024b8def3d5a5","tid":2491703,"uid":286199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"個口咁撚臭，奶到個閪都臭撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0b1692e0c01e043b63b28b0512bf7d52a3f8db","tid":2491703,"uid":27647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13: